        <Parent_String>closed automobiles [300227922], automobiles by form [300227921], automobiles [300178739], passenger vehicles [300227816], freewheeled vehicles by form or function [300227810], freewheeled vehicles [300227809], land vehicles by form [300215717], land vehicles [300212968], vehicles (transportation) [300219258], Transportation Vehicles (hierarchy name) [300042929], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
